📌 Playwright Locators List (with Description)
page.getByRole()
➤ Finds elements using ARIA roles (like button, textbox, link) + accessible name
➤ ✅ Most recommended & reliable
page.getByText()
➤ Locates elements based on visible text on the page
➤ ✅ Useful for buttons, links, static text
page.getByLabel()
➤ Finds form fields using associated label text
➤ ✅ Best for input fields (email, password, etc.)
page.getByPlaceholder()
➤ Targets input fields using placeholder text
➤ ✅ Useful when label is not available
page.getByAltText()
➤ Locates images using alt attribute text
➤ ✅ Used for image validation/testing
page.getByTitle()
➤ Finds elements using the title attribute
➤ ✅ Helpful for tooltips or extra info elements
page.getByTestId()
➤ Uses custom attribute like data-testid
➤ ✅ Highly stable for automation (preferred in real projects)